Now it’s easier and faster to check everything, from credit, info, even validity, on the new MyTelkomsel Dashboard! All in one screen, all done in a snap.

Want to switch accounts? Fret not, just swipe!
Whether it’s your Telkomsel, IndiHome, or Orbit account, you can access them all in one app. Plus, it’s now even easier to find exciting promos and explore your favorite features. 

MyTelkomsel is now faster to use and understand you even better!

BUYING PACKAGES IS HASSLE-FREE
You can now get personalized data plan recommendations based on your needs. Want to repurchase your favorite data plan or find the perfect roaming plan for your trip abroad? You just need one tap away!

Find the right data plan faster and hassle-free with clearer categories and simplified layouts.

FASTER PAYMENTS, SAFER ACCOUNT
Now with Telkomsel Wallet by GoPay, you can pay easily and store refund balance from your bank, all in one place. You can even use the balance right away to buy your favorite data plan.

Plus, your account is now more secure with PIN login. That means only you can access your MyTelkomsel account.

LOT OF PROMOS, MORE CHANCES TO SPEND MORE
In the For You section, you’ll find deals and packages picked just for you. Want extra savings? Don’t miss Flash Sale, full limited-time offers worth grabbing.
Need data for streaming, gaming, or staying productive? Just pick what suits you best!

YOUR LIFESTYLE NEEDS, ALL IN ONE APP
Who says MyTelkomsel is just about credit and data plans? Dive into entertainment and seamless transactions in the Lifestyle feature.
Through MyTelkomsel, you can explore powerful mini apps, from travel assistants to ticketing services.
Want to binge-watch exclusive and premium movies or short videos? You’ve got it, right in the app!
NEED HELP? JUST ASK VERO!
Stuck or got questions? No stress.
Veronika, your digital bestie, is here 24/7 to help out. She’s here to answer questions, fix issues, or just walk you through things.
Ask anything about Telkomsel, and Veronika’s here for you! Your go-to virtual assistant who truly gets you! 
READY TO MAKE YOUR DAY MORE FUN?
You can use this latest update for iOS 11.0 and above.
Got questions or want to share your ideas and suggestions? Head straight to https://tsel.me/FAQ for quick solutions, drop us a line at cs@telkomsel.com, or connect with us on any of our social media!

Bumble is the dating app where people meet, make connections, and start their love stories. We believe meaningful relationships are the foundation of a happy, healthy life — and we're here to help you find yours with a commitment to member safety and tools that empower confident dating.

- Our members are at the heart of everything we do

- See everyone who likes you

- Rematch with expired connections — so you don’t miss out on a great potential date

Inclusivity is key
At Bumble, we promise to support and include all forms of love: straight, gay, lesbian, queer, and beyond. We want everyone in our community to feel safe and welcome. So no matter how you identify, if you're looking for a place to chat, date, and find real love, we’ve got what you’re looking for.

HiWatchPro是一款基于蓝牙手环开发的app，使用蓝牙4.0通信，里面包统计睡眠、遥控拍照(通过手环拍照)，闹钟设置，久坐提醒（设置提醒时间防止用户坐太久），抬手亮屏、计步、消息推送、勿扰模式、睡眠监测、找手环等功能。用户可以利用app直观的了解身体状况以及运动状况，是一款轻量型助手型工具类app。


注意事项：
1，运动功能会使用GPS定位，在后台持续运行GPS功能可能会大幅消耗电池电量
2，HiWatchPro已接入HealthKit，可同步运行数据到健康
3，HiWatchPro所产生的一切数据，仅用于参考，不能当作健康状况依据。

"My Yamaha Motor" has been created for anyone who owns and rides a Yamaha Motorcycle.  
The app supports you to have more rewarding lifestyle with your Yamaha motorcycle.  

[1] IN DAILY LIFE 
- A portal to connect easily to the range of information or services you want. 
- Using smartphone GPS data and Yamaha dealership network info, you can locate the nearest dealership and can create a favorites list.  

[2] SERVICE SUPPORT 
- Having motorcycle registration in digital form, you won’t miss important information like free service coupons, etc. 
- The history of maintenance service for your motorcycle can be checked.  

[3] WHEN IN NEED 
- You can contact a dealership if you face trouble on the road.  
- You can contact directly to Yamaha if you have any inquiries.  
- For certain model owners, you also can call road service (YES24) for help. [Indonesia only] 

------------------- 
[SPECIFIC FUNCTIONS] 
VEHICLE REGISTRATION 
- Top page shows your Yamaha motorcycle information 
- You can register multiple models. You can also customize your registered motorcycle photo and nick name.  

WARRANTY & FREE SERVICE COUPON INFO 
- You can check warranty and free service coupon status.  
- You can also apply to use free service coupon by showing the app at dealership. [Vietnam only] 
- You can read model’s owner’s manual. [Indonesia only] 

SERVICE HISTORY 
- You can track detail history of maintenance service provided by Yamaha dealership.  

MESSAGES 
- The app sends you messages about service maintenance, free service coupons and other useful information.  

QUICK ASSIST (Indonesia: SKY) 
- The app shows nearest dealership automatically, so you can promptly contact to ask for help if you face trouble on the road.  

DEALERSHIP INFORMATION  
- You can search Yamaha dealerships based on various criteria, such as the nearest dealership or desired service. 
- You can mark your favorite dealerships for quick reference.   

LAUNCHER 
- You can easily access to other Yamaha-related apps and websites which are showed at home screen of the App.  

SETTING 
- You can check your profile, refer to list of FAQs. If it’s necessary, you can contact to Yamaha Call Center via the app. 

-------------------
CONFIRMED COMPATIBILITY WITH 
iOS 15 and UP
iPhone6s and UP

CONFIRMED USABLE DEVICES 
Smartphones 
*Compatibility/usability checks are conducted under set conditions. Please be aware that the app may not function properly with all smartphones or operating systems. 

NOTES ON USAGE
 - The app and its features are all free to use, but any fees resulting from downloading the app and any data transmitted while using the app will be borne by the user.
 - Creating an account with YamahaMotorID is required to use the app.
 - The app uses your smartphone’s GPS functions, which may drain battery life faster.
 - Some smartphones may not receive notifications due to battery or power-saving settings. Check your smartphone's user manual or provider for details. 

WARNING!
- Always stop the vehicle before operating your smartphone.
- Never take your hands off the handlebars while riding.
- Always concentrate on riding by keeping your eyes and mind on the road.
